    "본문HTML": "<p>\n\n</p><p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">1. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">장학명</span></span>: <span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">은평</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">삼천사 지역미래불자육성장학</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">2. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">후원사찰</span></span>: <span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">은평</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">삼천사</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">3. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">장학금</span></span>: <span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">100</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">만원</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">생활비성</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">                   ※ </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">타 불교계장학 이중수혜 불가</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(2026</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">학년도</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">                        (</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">동국건학장학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">총무원장학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">인서장학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">불교청년지도자육성장학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">월드머시코리아 장학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">지역미래불자육성장학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">4. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">선발 인원</span></span>: <span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">00</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">명</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">5. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">지원 자격</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">    ① </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.2pt;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">2026</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.2pt;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">학년도 </span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.2pt;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">1</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.2pt;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">학기 재학생</span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">으로서 </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.2pt;\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">서울 은평구 지역 </span></span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">주소지 </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">또는 해당 지역 고교 출신 학생</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">    ② </span></span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">불교동아리 부원이거나 가입 예정</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">인 학생</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">6. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">신청방법</span></span>: <span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[nDRIMS</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">접속</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">] </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">왼쪽상단</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">] </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">학생신청</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">]</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">신청함 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">장학</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">]</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">장학신청</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">교외</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">) </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">장학명</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">] </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[‘</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">삼천사</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">5</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">기</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">’ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">지역미래불자육성장학</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">] </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">선택 </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">자기소개서 작성</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:-0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">]</span></span> <span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">저장</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">] </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">→ </span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">[</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">제출</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">]</span></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">7. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">신청기한</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">:</span></span> <span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">~4.28.(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">화</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">) 23:59</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">까지</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">8. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">장학생 주요 의무 사항</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">     - </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">교내 장학증서 수여식 참석</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(5</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">월 </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">中 </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">예정</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">     - </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">감사편지 작성 및 불교동아리 활동</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">     - </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">교내 불교행사</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">연등행렬</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(5.16.), </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">영캠프</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(9</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">월</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)) </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">필수 참석</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">9. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">합격자 발표</span></span>: <span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">합격생에게만 개별 통보</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">10. </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">문의사항</span></span>: <span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">건학위 사무국 행정팀</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">(02-2260-8630, </span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">만해관 지하</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">1</span></span><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">층</span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:동국체;\">)</span></span></p>\n<div id=\"hwpEditorBoardContent\"> </div>",
    "본문": "1.\n장학명\n:\n(\n은평\n)\n삼천사 지역미래불자육성장학\n2.\n후원사찰\n:\n(\n은평\n)\n삼천사\n3.\n장학금\n:\n100\n만원\n(\n생활비성\n)\n※\n타 불교계장학 이중수혜 불가\n(2026\n학년도\n)\n(\n동국건학장학\n,\n총무원장학\n,\n인서장학\n,\n불교청년지도자육성장학\n,\n월드머시코리아 장학\n,\n지역미래불자육성장학\n)\n4.\n선발 인원\n:\n00\n명\n5.\n지원 자격\n①\n2026\n학년도\n1\n학기 재학생\n으로서\n서울 은평구 지역\n주소지\n또는 해당 지역 고교 출신 학생\n②\n불교동아리 부원이거나 가입 예정\n인 학생\n6.\n신청방법\n:\n[nDRIMS\n접속\n]\n→\n[\n왼쪽상단\n]\n→\n[\n학생신청\n]\n신청함\n→\n[\n장학\n]\n장학신청\n(\n교외\n)\n→\n[\n장학명\n]\n→\n[‘\n삼천사\n5\n기\n’\n지역미래불자육성장학\n]\n선택\n→\n[\n자기소개서 작성\n]\n→\n[\n저장\n]\n→\n[\n제출\n]\n7.\n신청기한\n:\n~4.28.(\n화\n) 23:59\n까지\n8.\n장학생 주요 의무 사항\n-\n교내 장학증서 수여식 참석\n(5\n월\n中\n예정\n)\n-\n감사편지 작성 및 불교동아리 활동\n-\n교내 불교행사\n(\n연등행렬\n(5.16.),\n영캠프\n(9\n월\n))\n필수 참석\n9.\n합격자 발표\n:\n합격생에게만 개별 통보\n10.\n문의사항\n:\n건학위 사무국 행정팀\n(02-2260-8630,\n만해관 지하\n1\n층\n)",
